description: Intense wind and rain flood streets and fell trees on islands in western Greece.
title: Medicane Storm Ianos lashes western Greece
title_page: Medicane Storm Ianos lashes western Greece - BBC News
maintext: The cyclone is moving eastwards, so at the weekend the winds - now up to 117km/h (73mph) - are set to hit the Peloponnese, then Athens and Crete.
